  "keyFeatures": [
    "Fast multi-threaded FASTQ extraction with fasterq-dump",
    "Prefetch and caching for SRA accessions from NCBI, AWS, and GCP",
    "Support for controlled-access dbGaP data via NGC files",
    "SRA Lite format support for reduced storage and faster downloads",
    "Alignment output in SAM/BAM format via sra-pileup",
    "NGS language bindings for C++, Java, and Python",
    "Cross-platform support for Linux, macOS, and Windows"
